SparsePulmoNet includes an adapted CRATE/Coding RAte reduction TransformEr image encoder.
The CRATE implementation is derived from the public MIT-licensed CRATE repository uploaded by the authors.
The original CRATE license is preserved in third_party/CRATE_LICENSE.

This code package is intended to make the SparsePulmoNet manuscript reproducible at the implementation level.
It does not redistribute the OSIC dataset. Users must download the dataset from the official Kaggle competition page and comply with its terms.
